OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early morning low cloud
OL,6,Fwill quickly burn away to leave
OL,7,Fanother dry and sunny day. The
OL,8,Fsunshine however maybe hazy at times,
OL,9,Fwith the brisk breeze continuing
OL,10,Facross southern hills and coasts.
OL,11,FFeeling very warm, especially inland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining fine and dry this
OL,14,Fevening with plenty of late sunshine.
OL,15,FLittle change overnight with largely
OL,16,Fclear skies. A warm night, especially
OL,17,Fin the towns and cities.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
