OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,6,Fonce any early morning low cloud and
OL,7,Fmist clears. Feeling very warm,
OL,8,Fespecially in the strong sunshine.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FRemaining largely dry and settled
OL,12,Fthroughout. A small chance of a few
OL,13,Fshowers at times, but most will avoid
OL,14,Fthem. Very warm initially but a little
OL,15,Fcooler by Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
